        List<Integer> list(UUID datasetKey,
                 org.gbif.api.model.common.paging.Pageable page)
        A simple paging query for all usages in checklistbank. We only return name usage ids here to avoid extremely heavy operations for the database when the offset gets bigger.
        Returns:
        the name usage ids belonging to the requested page.
